# CineVerse Backend - Environment Configuration
# To enable REAL-TIME payments instead of Mock mode:
# 1. Rename this file from `.env.example` to `.env`
# 2. Sign up at https://razorpay.com/ and generate your Live/Test API Keys
# 3. Paste them below!

RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_real_key_id_here
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_real_key_secret_here

# When these keys are detected automatically by the server, real transactions will be processed!
